{
  "stem": "12462.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One day, I was in court, and Justice Jackson, or his son, had asked me to be there to accompany Senator Claude Pepper of Florida, who was over visiting.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And since-- since Pepper was on the Foreign Relations Committee, naturally, he had some influence.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they wanted someone to accompany him into the courtroom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I actually took him into the courtroom on about the fourth day of the trial.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we sat at the prosecution table, back a ways from the-- the main prosecutors, who were going to present things to the tribunal, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [CLEARS THROAT] I was looking at the dock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I saw that Goering was writing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he took his-- he broke his pencil.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he took it and threw it down on the dock and sat there like this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I went up to the guard beside him and handed the guard a new pencil.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said, Goering broke his pencil.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Give him a pencil.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The guard did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I went back and sat down at the prosecution table.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Immediately thereafter, the court declared a recess.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And Senator Pepper and I stood up between the [CLEARS THROAT] main prosecution table where he'd been sitting in the dock.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were talking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I had my back to the dock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And suddenly, I could notice that the Senator Pepper was bobbing his head around.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He says, Goering is motioning toward you, and the guard is not objecting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I turned around, and I walked over toward the dock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- [CLEARS THROAT] Goering said to me, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He bowed and said, I thank you, very much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I thank you, very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said to him, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You're very welcome.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You're very welcome.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
